Our Roadmap

PHASE 1
Awareness

We need to build more awareness of what we all share on this earth, We are all related, and if you believe in PSI Coin and keeping our earth green, you have one more thing in common with your fellow man. The Whitepaper can help your friends and family to open a crypto wallet and get this token on Uniswap. You may buy the Earth's most precious products on our websites or trade psi coin for other coins.

PHASE 2
Token Distribution

We will provide free tokens to those who assist in spreading Psi coin on all social media platforms. See more details on "How to receive free Psi coin" on our website.

PHASE 3
Our Plans

After two months of raising the necessary funds, we plan to launch our products and services, and we will also update our community about our new products and who is part this online community of crypto users and Earth menders. Six months or sooner from launch day based solely on supporting funds we will start a newsletter of current progress of toucancoin course of action to save Earth's precious resources, and add more products and services that can be purchased online.

PHASE 4
Our Plans

Within 11 months, the project (depending on support and available funds for the project) we will accumulate 10% net worth and invest it back in the Earth.

PHASE 4
Our Plans

Psi coin is a group of business owners and families who want to create a change in the way we respect our Earth.
The Covid-19 pandemic and other unexpected natural events across the world have caused us to ask ourselves what can we do to contribute to the future of humankind and our damaged and incomplete world?

How to Buy?

1- Create MetaMask wallet

Create a meta mask wallet using either a desktop computer or an iOS/android mobile service. That will allow you to buy, sell, and receive PSI coins.

2- Send ETH to your wallet

Send ETH to your wallet. You can buy Ethereum (ETH) directly on MetaMask or transfer it to your MetaMask Wallet from exchanges like Coinbase, Binance, etc. Make sure to use the ERC-20 network when transfering ETH.

3- Connect your wallet to Uniswap

Connect your wallet to Uniswap Access your wallet to Uniswap by clicking ‘Connect to a wallet’ and selecting MetaMask.

4- Swap ETH for PSI Coin

Swap ETH for PSI coin You can start swapping as soon as you have ETH available! Press ‘Select a token’ and enter the token address or search for it on the tokens list.
